data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! Check out this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 2-car garage home. The home features a brand-new roof, A/C & water heater. This gorgeous home features plenty of entertaining space along with a split floor plan with a grand living room and vaulted ceilings. This home has a stunning fully remodeled kitchen featuring granite countertops and beautiful cabinets. As you walk into this HUGE master bedroom you will be amazed at the size of the room. The master bathroom has been remodeled as well. You will find the other bedrooms will be on the opposite side of the house. Sharing the second bathroom. The exterior offers serene privacy with NO REAR NEIGHBORS and a conservation lot on one side. It is conveniently located just minutes from Poinciana Hospital, schools, and shopping/restaurants. This could be your new home or a great investment property. To schedule your private or virtual tour, reach out today! The property does have solar panels in place, saving you money on your utility bill!
